<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><span style="line-height: 17.12px;"><br>I’ve not been able to reach you today regarding your request for an insurance quote via our partner, Tradeshake.<br><br></span></font><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">As a client of Tradeshake, you are entitled to a discount of 10% off our standard business insurance package.</b><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px;"><br></span><br>It will only take 5-10 minutes to provide you with a comprehensive quote.&nbsp;<a href="https://calendly.com/d/cqx7-zw6-htm/kingsbridge-insurance-call-back-tradeshake" style="font-weight: bold;">Book a call with me today.</a><b><br></b><b><br></b>Here at Kingsbridge we offer a complete package of cover that is designed specifically for UK businesses. Our comprehensive package includes&nbsp;<b>Public Liability</b>,&nbsp;<b>Goods and Tools cover</b>, and&nbsp;<b>Employers’ Liability&nbsp;</b>(if required).&nbsp;<br><br><b>Why buy with Kingsbridge?</b></font></p><ul style="font-size: 12pt;"><li style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Nil excess*&nbsp;</b>- guarantees no unexpected out-of-pocket expenses in the event of a claim.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Tools cover included at no extra cost</b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;- feel safe with 24-hour cover and new for old replacements for any thefts or accidents. Plus, a next business day payment after your claim is agreed.</span></font></font></li><li style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Height work accepted</b>&nbsp;- with specific limits subject to job role.</font></li><li style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Hot Work accepted&nbsp;</b>- across all trades including grinders, blow torches, hot air guns and more.</font></li></ul><p style="font-size: 12pt;"></p><p style="font-size: 12pt;"></p><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">So, I can discuss with you which parts of the policy would be relevant for your business, it would be great to speak over the phone.</span></font><font style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;<a href="https://calendly.com/d/cqx7-zw6-htm/kingsbridge-insurance-call-back-tradeshake" style="font-weight: bold;">Book a call with me.</a><b><br></b></font><b style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Alternatively, you can&nbsp;</span></font>reply to let me know a good time to call or&nbsp;<font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">contact me on</span></font><b style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;01242 808 740</b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">. Our office is open between the hours of 8:00am-5:30pm, Monday-Friday.&nbsp;</span></font><br><br><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">I look forward to hearing from you.&nbsp;</span></font><br><br><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; background-color: white;">Kind regards,</span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;</span></font><br><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Sales Team</span></font><br><br><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk</span></font><br><font style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">01242 808740</font></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">*Nil Excess applicable to Public Liability and Goods and Tools Cover only.&nbsp;</font></div>]]></td>
</tr>
